OL,3,CWhy are 50,000 oysters being dropped
OL,4,Cin St Helier Harbour?
OL,6,FThey can also help reduce harmful
OL,7,Femissions by trapping carbon dioxide
OL,8,Fin their shells and shoring up
OL,9,Fsediments.
OL,11,FOther benefits include acting as
OL,12,Fnatural barriers against erosion and
OL,13,Fboosting local biodiversity.
OL,15,FThey have been placed beneath Albert
OL,16,FPier, under the St Helier Marina
OL,17,Faccess ramp and next to the
OL,18,Faccommodation pods with regular
OL,19,Fmonitoring to check how the initiative
OL,20,Fis going.
