OL,3,CWhy are 50,000 oysters being dropped
OL,4,Cin St Helier Harbour?
OL,6,FHead of Maritime Operations, Louise
OL,7,FStafford, says: "Oysters, small but
OL,8,Fmighty, possess an incredible ability
OL,9,Fto filter water.
OL,11,F"We are aiming to harness this natural
OL,12,Fskill to further improve water quality
OL,13,Fin the harbour."
OL,15,FChris Le Masurier, owner of Jersey
OL,16,FOyster Company which is working with
OL,17,FPorts on the project, adds: "This
OL,18,Finitiative not only highlights the
OL,19,Fremarkable natural abilities of
OL,20,Foysters but also underscores our
OL,21,Fcommitment to sustainability.
